es.us.isa.aml.translator.builders.wsag.model

Class ServiceLevelObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.us.isa.aml.translator.builders.wsag.model.ServiceLevelObjective

  • public class ServiceLevelObjective
extends java.lang.Object
    The Service Level Objective element in a guarantee term is also expressed as an assertion over service attributes and/or external factors such as date, time. However, most often a Service Level Objective is expressed as a target for a Key Performance Indicator (KPI) such as average response time, completion time, availability, etc.

    jdelafuente
